Package: libdaemon-dev
Version: 0.14-r0.70
Description: Lightweight C library which eases the writing of UNIX daemons - Development files
 Lightweight daemon framework for OpenBSD. It provides facilities for
 logging and a signal handler to enable graceful shutdown, as well as file
 locking to ensure that only a single copy of a given daemon is running at
 a time.  This package contains symbolic links, header files, and related
 items necessary for software development.
